sect1:
Installing Grep-&grep-version;



The Grep package contains programs for searching through files.

Estimated build time:           &grep-time;
Estimated required disk space:  &grep-compsize;

&aa-grep-down;
&aa-grep-dep;

 
 


Installation of Grep


Prepare Grep for compilation:

./configure --prefix=/usr --bindir=/bin \
    --with-included-regex


Compile the package:

make


This package has a test suite available which can perform a number of
checks to ensure it built correctly.  Should you choose to run it, the 
following command will do so:

make check


And install the package:

make install



